      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "臣等见驾，吾皇万岁。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00016",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "正在龙床来养静，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00017",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "昏昏沉沉有人声。睁开了昏花眼强自扎挣，",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00018",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "先生！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00019",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "主公！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00020",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "四弟！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00021",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "赵云"
      ],
      "text": "万岁！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00022",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "啊，众卿哪……",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00023",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "同哭",
      "speakers": [
        "马良",
        "马谡",
        "赵云",
        "邓芝",
        "费祎",
        "二太子",
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "万岁呀……",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00024",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "抬头只见众公卿。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00025",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "主公，自觉龙体如何？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00026",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "先生哪。孤患此疾，只恐死在旦夕。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00027",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "主公切须保重龙体才是。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00028",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "先生有治国大才，比曹丕胜强十倍，当能安邦定国。嗣子懦弱，当扶则扶；如若不才，先生你、你、你就自己消受了罢。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00029",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀主公啊！多蒙主公三顾之恩，臣纵肝脑涂地，鞠躬尽瘁，死而后已！",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00030",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "诸葛亮哭。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00031",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "好个忠义的先生！二皇儿过来。尔弟兄三人，以父事丞相，不可怠慢，向前拜过先生，以为相父。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00032",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。二太子同拜。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00033",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "谢主龙恩。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00034",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "张苞，命你将你父的尸首搬回阆中安葬去罢。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00035",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张苞"
      ],
      "text": "遵命。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00036",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张苞下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00037",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "关兴听令：命你带领三千人马，抵挡吴兵。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00038",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关兴"
      ],
      "text": "得令。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00039",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关兴下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00040",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "唉！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00041",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "从前不听先生言，损兵折将也枉然。马到临崖收缰晚，船到江心……",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00042",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "唉！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00043",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "补漏难哪……",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00044",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘备哭。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00045",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "事到临头才知悔，自己错了埋怨谁？楚霸王他不听范增语，乌江岸前把命逼。曹孟德中原成大器，他人的奸诈有谁知？阿斗年幼终何用，还望先生费心机。",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00046",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "先生哪。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00047",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "主公不必泪悲啼，为臣言来奏主知：蒙主公三顾之恩义，鞠躬尽瘁死而后已。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00048",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "叹先生说此话世间稀，二皇儿近前来细听端的：待先生如同待父意，他保阿斗立帝基。二皇儿近前来搀父体，",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00049",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘备下位。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00050",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "手搀先生泪悲啼。孤还有紧要事嘱咐你，还望先生牢记心里。头一件扫荡中原地，第二要恢复汉室基。哭一声懦弱的汉献帝，四百载基业化灰泥。",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00051",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵云"
      ],
      "text": "万岁还须保龙体，臣等保主不敢欺。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00052",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "回头又见赵四弟，你的功劳王尽知。自从患难来相聚，又谁知今日两分离。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00053",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "众位卿家。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00054",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "马良",
        "马谡",
        "赵云",
        "邓芝",
        "费祎",
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "万岁。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00055",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "邓芝！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00056",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "邓芝"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00057",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "马良！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00058",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马良"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00059",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "众位卿家请站起，叫声邓芝、马良和费祎。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "05007005_e00060",
      "play_id": "05007005",
      "scene_id": "05007005_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
